# Hello Hackers 

## Intro to Commands 
This challenge allowed us to learn the commands and type out our first command on pwn.college. We learnt about the basic starting commands in Linux.

### My Solution 
**Flag:** `pwn.college{Er3QjqO_HooM7j_VQgyzDPYOJUT.QX4YjM1wyN1QzNzEzW}`
By simply typing 'hello' in the command prompt we got the Flag and hence completed our first task. 

```bash
hacker@hello~intro-to-commands:~$ hello
Success! Here is your flag:
pwn.college{k67a4WQq_cDaiotf9CPCxJaJKUd.QX3YjM1wyN1QzNzEzW}
```

### My learnings 
We learnt how a terminal in Linux works and how with just simple and easy commands we can type out our input in Linux command prompt window.

